### _sp_sv_weapon_switch

_sp_sv_weapon_switch

Bestweap weapon switching behaviour.

Values:

- 0: Let the player decide with his bestweap settings (default)
- 1: Force bestweap to none
- 2: Force bestweap to safe
- 3: Force bestweap to unsafe
- 4: Switch to the newest weapon; Not implemented yet!
